## 🛠️ Stack & Rules
- **Framework**: Expo SDK v56.0.0, React Native, Expo Router.
- **Routing**: File-based routing under `src/app`.
  - Group `(auth)` contains login & register.
  - Group `(tabs)` contains main screens (home, explore, profile).
- **Paths**: Use `@/` path alias for all imports inside `src/`.
- **Database**: Uses SQLite via `expo-sqlite` on native (`src/database/db.ts`) and AsyncStorage on web (`src/database/db.web.ts`).
